kde-fan-control (1.0.4-1) questing; urgency=medium

  * Fix critical bug: applying any draft setting caused all previously-managed
    fans to lose their PID control and revert to maximum speed (PWM 255).
    The apply-draft transaction now correctly preserves ownership for fans
    carried over from the previous applied config.
  * Add #[serde(default)] to DraftFanEntry.managed for forward-compatible
    TOML deserialization.

 -- Samiran Amiran <sherwin@amiran.us>  Wed, 16 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000

kde-fan-control (1.0.3-1) questing; urgency=medium

  * Fix polkit authorization: send uid as INT32 (not UINT32) and
    start-time as raw clock ticks (not microseconds).

 -- Samiran Amiran <sherwin@amiran.us>  Wed, 15 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000

